{"url": "https://mashable.com/2018/07/24/tom-cruise-jimmy-fallon-mad-lib/", "text": "Jimmy Fallon and Tom Cruise have done their fair share of silly skits on The Tonight Show over the years. And their newly made-up Mission: Impossible scene is just as harebrained.\n\nIn a segment on Monday night's show, Fallon and Cruise acted out a dramatic spy movie scene they'd written together playing the \"Mad Lib\" game. Adhering to the segment rules, Cruise answers Fallon's random questions, and then the two use them as dialogue in a made-up movie scene.\n\nCruise's answers are quite bizarre \u2014 his response to a hypothetical spider crawling up his leg was a cool \"come here, darling,\" \u2014 so make for a pretty strange scene. But it's worth watching just for the pair to try and keep a straight face during their fictional train ride.\n\nWant more Mad Lib Theater? Check out older versions by John Cena, Benedict Cumberbatch and Chris Pratt for starters.", "images": ["https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/00RI0gmJ4d9TOzf8DrlcVvQ/hero-image.fill.size_220x220.v1763486628.jpg", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/00xMcBbCxmvuO0sQ0dk4loD/hero-image.fill.size_220x220.v1763638525.png", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/01rRBjumvWiE0CqhiG5jEj4/hero-image.fill.size_220x133.v1758279779.png", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/013bZ6S7YJOMaoZKvFaMTgG/hero-image.fill.size_220x220.v1763461362.png", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/00RI0gmJ4d9TOzf8DrlcVvQ/hero-image.fill.size_220x133.v1763486628.jpg", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/048QIsgZ5EnksL05lhqZJdp/hero-image.fill.size_220x133.v1760428393.png", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/authors/03ViZY8xuP4VcGszqNHGLjV/image.fill.size_100x100.v1763636998.png", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/videos/05umsf9vBeWxHEyF1apcB56/hero-image.fill.size_220x133.v1759828165.jpg", "https://helios-i.mashable.com/imagery/authors/03ViZY8xuP4VcGszqNHGLjV/image.fill.size_512x512